      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The project goal is to make a personal site hosted on the internet. The three main components of this site are Hugo static site generator and wowchemy Academic template and GitHub hosting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
