&lt;p&gt;The site home page contains my profile picture, biography, information about education, skills, experience and my posts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;hugo&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A static site generator takes your content, applies it to a template, and generates an HTML based static site. It’s excellent for blogs and landing pages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Benefits:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quick deployment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Secure (no dynamic content)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fast load times&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Simple usage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Version control&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To start with Hugo first i downloaded the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/releases&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;last version&lt;/a&gt; of Hugo. Then i created a new repository cloned from Wowchemy academic template. After cloning the repository and creating a new repository to host the site. I generated the site using Hugo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;wowchemy&#34;&gt;Wowchemy&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Wowchemy Hugo academic template help to create  the site and supply the neded file to us so we can customize it and work on it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
