&lt;p&gt;Simply cloned the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/maabedelhay/starter-hugo-academic&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;template&lt;/a&gt; as a new repository.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;github&#34;&gt;Github&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;GitHub free hosting is the main allowed us to host the site on the internet. by creating a repository in the form of username.github.io. In this repository the coded of the site.&lt;/p&gt;
