&lt;h2 id=&#34;this-project-helped-me-to-understand-how-github-hosting-work-how-important-to-have-a-personal-blog-that-push-you-to-post-your-work-and-ideas&#34;&gt;This project helped me to understand how GitHub hosting work. How important to have a personal blog that push you to post your work and ideas.&lt;/h2&gt;
